me zones.andP;  These maps are given by region, group, continent,or world view.andM;The data can be exported to programs such as PC-PaintBrush, WordPerfect,PageMaker, Ventura, and Lotus1-2-3.andP;  It captures screens in PCX format andcan output data as ASCII files.andP;  These output files make it possible to usethe data in many ways.andM;PUMA RATINGandM;PERFORMANCE: (3.7) Performs as advertised.andP;  Of course, I'd like to be able tochange database information for future reference.andM;USEFULNESS: (4) For all it provides this program is really quite reasonablypriced.andM;MANUAL: (4) Documentation is sufficient and the most features are selfexplanatory.andM;AVAILABILITY: (4) PC-Globe is seen in many computer stores.andP;  It can beordered directly from PC-Globe via phone with VISA, Mastercard, or AMEX from800-255-2789.andP;  PC-Globe will, also, accept payment for an order with a check,money order, or COD.andP;  A DEMO can be had for $3.andM;(tbass, HNDYPRSN/19901010/Press Contact: Richard Burger, 602-730- 9000)</TEXT></DOC>